WEBVTT

00:00:59.823 --> 00:01:04.298
I was filled with anxiety and guilt
and shame all the time,

00:01:04.322 --> 00:01:06.121
and I didn't know why.

00:01:06.145 --> 00:01:09.200
I hated my body, I hated myself,

00:01:09.224 --> 00:01:10.970
I got sick a lot,

00:01:10.994 --> 00:01:12.300
I couldn't think,

00:01:12.324 --> 00:01:13.946
I couldn't remember things.

00:01:14.343 --> 00:01:17.545
I was drawn to dangerous men and women

00:01:17.569 --> 00:01:22.438
who I allowed -- actually, I invited --
to treat me badly,

00:01:22.462 --> 00:01:25.276
because that is what my father
taught me love was.

00:01:26.708 --> 00:01:31.237
I waited my whole life
for my father to apologize to me.